item.title: Server Project
item.dc:creator: @mod_taharok Taharok
item.description:
@mod_taharok wrote:

Lol I am a coder and I would say definatly Testscape is your best guess. P16 v6’s auto save is broken and a lot of bugs are in it. Cheezscape is a lessened Testscape. So you want Testscape because of all of the adjicments on it compared to Cheezscape. Just add an auto-saver to the Testscape server and add/remove/edit a few commonly used things on the server and there ya go! Testscape is the best server to modify and its bugs really are not that bad. =)
